meta.name: redis
meta.description: Dashboard for the telegraf input plug-in: Redis
meta.author: influxdata

queries.query: SELECT mean("clients") AS "clients" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."redis" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
SELECT mean("blocked_clients") AS "blocked_clients" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."redis" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("used_cpu_user")) AS "used_cpu_per_second" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."redis" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("used_memory")) AS "used_memory_per_second" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."redis" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
